me comes in four sizes and three vampire-themed colors. It is available now in select colr and size combinations. You pick from Twilight white, Coffin Nail black, or bright Blood red. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vampire-Fastarossa-DH-bike-low-mid-high-pivot-adjustable-CF3-suspension_prototype-DH-race-build.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vampire-Fastarossa-DH-bike-low-mid-high-pivot-adjustable-CF3-suspension_prototype-DH-race-build.webp\" alt=\"Vampire Fastarossa DH bike low mid high pivot adjustable CF3 suspension, Chris Canfield downhill prototype\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vampire-Fastarossa-DH-bike-low-mid-high-pivot-adjustable-CF3-suspension_prototype-DH-race-build.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vampire-Fastarossa-DH-bike-low-mid-high-pivot-adjustable-CF3-suspension_prototype-DH-race-build-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vampire-Fastarossa-DH-bike-low-mid-high-pivot-adjustable-CF3-suspension_prototype-DH-race-build-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vampire-Fastarossa-DH-bike-low-mid-high-pivot-adjustable-CF3-suspension_prototype-DH-race-build-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Vampire-Fastarossa-DH-bike-low-mid-high-pivot-adjustable-CF3-suspension_prototype-DH-race-build-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And then Chris Canfield will help get you set up with the fork &amp; shock of your choice to start your perfect build.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.vampire.bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Vampire.bike</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/vampire-fastarossa-debuts-wild-3-in-1-dh-suspension-from-chris-canfields-beautiful-mind/\">Vampire Fastarossa Debuts Wild 3-in-1 DH Suspension from Chris Canfield’s Beautiful Mind</a> appe